title: GOP lawmaker hears demands for 'a fighter' for speaker
text: > Texas GOP lawmaker hears demands for 'a fighter' for speaker Rep. Blake Farenthold, R-Texas, holds a town hall meeting Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Wharton, Texas. As he travels his southeast Texas district this week, Farenthold has a message for his constituents: Despite appearances, the House GOP is not in disarray. His voters, in turn, have a message for him: Good riddance to the current slate of GOP leaders, and find a new speaker who will stand up for conservative values. (AP Photo/Pat Sullivan)
